Class DefaultColorShapeRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.ui.helpers.DefaultColorShapeRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphColorShapeRepository

    public class DefaultColorShapeRepository
extends Object
implements GraphColorShapeRepository
    The Graph Shape Repository is responsible for serving as a single point of storage and retrieval for NamedShape throughout the SEMOSS system (shapes in graphs and in graph-legends, such as lists and combo-boxes).
    Author:
    Wayne Warren
